data.title: Liv Tyler pregnant with second child
data.meta_description: The 37-year-old actress is already a mom to 9-year-old son Milo
data.text:
Liv Tyler is pregnant for the second time, according to multiple reports.

The 37-year-old actress has yet to comment on the news, but both People and E! News confirm that she's with baby.

The "Leftovers" star is already mom to 9-year-old son Milo William Langdon from her previous marriage to musician Royston Langdon. They were married from 2003-2009.

She's most recently been attached to British football agent Dave Gardner, David Beckham's good friend. Gardner appeared in the documentary "David Beckham into the Unknown."

Tyler and Gardner have been spotted out together over the past few months.
